{"type":"message","id":"39dd8923","parentId":"d3e8a647","timestamp":"2026-04-02T19:00:00.875Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:55a9fce0-aec0-4dbc-b7cc-c7066c77d995 每日自动更新检查] 执行以下更新检查并推送摘要：1）运行 `clawhub update --all` 检查已安装 skills 的可更新情况（若因本地改动/可疑技能/缺失技能而跳过，明确写出原因）；2）不要使用 `npm update -g clawdbot@latest --dry-run`，改为只读版本检查：输出本机 `openclaw --version`，再查询 npm 上 `openclaw` 最新版本，判断是否存在新版本；3）不要实际更新 OpenClaw 本体。报告检查结果。\nCurrent time: Friday, April 3rd, 2026 — 3:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-02 19:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775156400871}}
