exity. I might want to clarify the reasons for the first run abort and mention the current installed list count of 18 as well.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Updating OpenClaw versions**\\n\\nI need to mention the OpenClaw versions: the local version is 2026.3.28 (f9b1079), while the latest available via npm is 2026.4.1. It’s clear that a newer version exists, but per my instructions, I'm not updating OpenClaw itself right now. I should include a note like \\\"本轮未执行 openclaw 本体更新\\\" to emphasize that the core OpenClaw update hasn’t been executed in this round. It's just important to keep everything clear!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"每日自动更新检查结果（2026-04-03 03:00 Asia/Shanghai）\n\n1. Skills 检查结果\n先执行了 `clawhub update --all`，但该命令在检查到 `stock-daily-report` 时因 “Skill not found” 中断。\n随后我做了分项补查（逐个 `clawhub update <skill>`），拿到了完整结果。\n\n已实际更新：\n- context-memory-optimizer：1.0.2 -> 1.0.5\n- xiaohongshu-search-summarizer：CLI 报告“updated -> 1.0.3”，当前安装版本显示仍为 1.0.3\n- xiaohongshu-skill：CLI 报告“updated -> 1.0.2”，当前安装版本显示仍为 1.0.2\n\n因本地改动跳过：\n- multi-search-engine\n- ddg-web-search\n- image-ocr-reader\n- memos\n- self-improving-agent\n- auto-updater\n- mcporter-skill\n- skill-vetter\n- claudecode-websearch\n- openclaw-backup\n- openclaw-spirits\n\n原因：这些技能都返回了 `local changes (no match). Use --force to overwrite.`，说明本地文件与仓库版本不一致，未强制覆盖。\n\n因可疑技能标记跳过：\n- todo-tracker\n- skill-creator\n- xiaohongshu-mcp\n\n原因：被 VirusTotal Code Insight 标记为 suspicious，CLI 默认未更新，提示需 `--force`。\n\n因缺失/无法定位而失败：\n- stock-daily-report\n\n原因：返回 `Skill not found`，这也是 `clawhub update --all` 首次中断的直接原因。\n\n本轮检查后当前安装版本中，明确发生版本提升的只有：\n- context-memory-optimizer：现为 1.0.5\n\n2. OpenClaw 本体版本检查（只读，未更新）\n- 本机版本：OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079)\n- npm 最新版本：2026.4.1\n\n判断：\n- 存在新版本\n- 按要求，本轮未实际更新 OpenClaw 本体\n\n3. 结论\n- Skills 侧：本轮有 1 个技能确认升级成功（context-memory-optimizer），2 个技能被 CLI 重新处理但未看到版本号变化，11 个因本地改动跳过，3 个因可疑标记跳过，1 个因 “Skill not found” 失败\n- OpenClaw 本体：有新版本可用，但本轮仅做检查，未执行更新","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02cc338cb0c318620169cebd75a9bc819aa281405c20eebf44\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":414,"output":1217,"cacheRead":33536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35167,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775156575968,"responseId":"resp_02cc338cb0c318620169cebd615e90819ab825cf38766161f4"}}
